# ===========================================
# NOTES
# ===========================================
# 
# 1. LOCAL DEVELOPMENT:
#    - Run: npm run db:start
#    - Use the local credentials above (they're the same for everyone)
#    - Local database is isolated and safe to experiment with
#
# 2. PRODUCTION:
#    - Comment out LOCAL section
#    - Uncomment PRODUCTION section
#    - Add your real Supabase credentials
#    - Never commit production keys to git!
#
# 3. GETTING LOCAL CREDENTIALS:
#    Run: npm run db:status
#    Copy the values shown in the output
#
# 4. SWITCHING ENVIRONMENTS:
#    Simply comment/uncomment the relevant section
#    No need to change code!